Sales Data Analysis Project (Excel)
 Project Overview

This project simulates a real-world business scenario where a Junior Data Analyst analyzes raw sales data to generate meaningful insights.

The goal is to understand regional performance and identify top-performing products using Excel.
Business Scenario
I worked as a Junior Data Analyst for a retail company.
The sales team provided raw sales data and requested analysis of regional performance.

Objectives
Clean the raw data
Calculate Total Revenue
Analyze revenue by Region and Category
Identify Top 5 products by revenue
Visualize data using charts

Tools Used
Microsoft Excel
Pivot Tables
Basic Excel Formulas

Steps Performed
1. Data Cleaning
Removed duplicate records
Handled missing values
Removed extra spaces using TRIM function
Ensured correct data formats (Date, Number)

2. Revenue Calculation

Created a new column:
Revenue = Quantity × Unit Price

3. Pivot Table Analysis
* Revenue by Region
Used Pivot Table
Grouped by Region
Calculated total revenue

* Revenue by Category
Grouped by Product Category
Calculated total revenue

4. Top 5 Products
Created Pivot Table with Product and Revenue
Sorted data in descending order
Applied Top 5 filter

5. Data Visualization
Created Column Chart
Visualized Revenue by Region
Helped in understanding performance easily

--Key Insights
Identified highest performing region
Found top revenue-generating products
Compared category-wise performance
Outcome

This project helped me understand:

Data cleaning techniques
Excel formulas
Pivot Tables
Data visualization

